everyone she met. Though she’s gone, she’d remain alive in our hearts forever. “I miss you, my sweetheart, and my most beautiful girl, Evelyn Murray-Bruce. Forever yours.” In minutes, Nigerians have sent condolence messages to on Twitter to the Senator. I’m broken. Just lost my beautiful wife to cancer. She was my best friend for 43 years and my wife for 41 years. Cancer is real, but it shouldn’t be a death sentence – awareness, and early detection and treatment are key to survival. I miss her so so much. I’m broken. pic.twitter.com/MPTTBhsGnB — Ben Murray-Bruce (@benmurraybruce) March 20, 2020  Vanguard Senator representing Bayelsa East, Ben Murray-Bruce and his amiable wife, Evelyn Murray-Bruce   are currently in a celebratory mood. September 7, 2018 In "Showtime People" The senator representing Bayelsa East constituency has on Monday withdrawn from the senatorial race. October 1, 2018 In "News" Following the demise of Senator Ben Uwajumogu on Wednesday morning, the House of Representatives and indeed, the senate may adjourn plenary till Friday. December 18, 2019 In "News"